<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Gallery_SavingSharingCreations" s="316037">
  <T n="name">0x411F7960<!--String: "Sharing & Saving Your Creations"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_SavingAndSharingYourCreations_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d7c111e4ff4e0ffc</T>
      <T n="text">0x53B0DBA6<!--String: "You can <b><font color='#199C2C'>save</font></b> your creations to your Library for future use, or save and <b><font color='#199C2C'>share</font></b> to the Gallery, so other players can download them!\n\nTo save or share a Household from Create a Sim, select the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Save Household</font></b> button.\n\nTo save or share a Room or Lot from Build Mode, select the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Save to My Library</font></b> in the toolbar, and then either <b><font color='#199C2C'>Save Lot</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>Save Room</font></b>. A Room must be selected with the Select tool for this option to be available."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_SavingAndSharingYourCreations_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d7c111e4ff4e0fff</T>
      <T n="text">0x8137B509<!--String: "This will open a window in which you can enter a <b><font color='#199C2C'>title</font></b> and a <b><font color='#199C2C'>description</font></b> of your creation. \n\nOnce you’re done, either Save to My Library or Share to the Gallery (sharing will also save the creation to My Library). \n\nUse hashtags in the description to help other players to find it!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_SavingAndSharingYourCreations_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d7c111e4ff4e0ffe</T>
      <T n="text">0x24B775F9<!--String: "Creations that you’ve saved to My Library can be <b><font color='#199C2C'>shared later</font></b>.\n\nSimply open the My Library tab, select your creation, and use the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Share to the Gallery</font></b> button."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Gallery\Gallery_SavingAndSharingYourCreations_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:d7c111e4ff4e0ff9</T>
      <T n="text">0x27D138D1<!--String: "You can view all your <b><font color='#199C2C'>shared creations</font></b> in your <b><font color='#199C2C'>Profile</font></b> by selecting the View Catalog button.\n\nIf you want to <b><font color='#199C2C'>remove</font></b> a creation from the Gallery, you can use the Remove from Gallery button in the lower left corner. If the creation is also saved in My Library, it will remain there."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_Gallery</E>
    <E>Lesson_ChildAccountRestricted</E>
  </L>
